reviewText:
Subpar acting. Script is corny at times. For a better 1957 trucking movie check out "Hell Drivers".
Also good quality but no extras.
because peter graves is one of my favourite actors for many years even though he has now passed away recently.
Yes this was surprisingly good.  And Chuck Connor was in this one, even though he was convincing as a hip dude.  It still was good. Nice surprise ending.

Warner Archive have done B movie fans a real favor by releasing this
classic B picture in a remastered widescreen version.
Fast furious fun and highly recommended.
